Dear Paul

.ue 2
                                                                      $..#$
Forts.: <2 Febr 69>*
I was glad to hear by your note that you are well; papa is not yet well, on
Sunday his going to Stamheim has renewed the cold so that to day he could
not go to Nagold; but had to send a Telegram, I hope that after a few days
he shall be free.

In Calw there are many sick peopel, every day one or two are burried.

                              Adieu dear Son
.fo -
                                      Yours J.G.


